instructions: Put the dinner plate in the center of the table cloth
Place the salad plate in on top of the dinner plate in the center
Place the folded napking on top of the salad plate in the center of the table cloth
place the wine glass on the upper right corner of the table cloth
Place the wine glass to the upper left of the water glass
Place the salad fork to the left of the dinner plate with prongs pointing upwards
Place the dinner fork between the salad fork and dinner plate with the prongs pointing upwards
Place the dinner knife to the right of the dinner plate with the blade pointed toward the plate
